  <brief_title>Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Tacrolimus Ointment in Treating Chronic Allergic Contact Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Vehicle-Controlled, Multicenter Trial to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of 0.1% Tacrolimus Ointment in the Treatment of Chronic Allergic Contact Dermatitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
