  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study of subjects with a known nickel allergy comparing Tacrolimus to placebo, both
      associated with nickel patches to determine the safety and efficacy of treating Chronic
      Allergic Contact Dermatitis with Tacrolimus Ointment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
